---
// Banner CTA final — claim + llamada a la acción
---

<section
  class="px-6 py-28 md:py-36"
  style="background-color: var(--color-brand-yellow); background-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at 15% 50%, rgba(138, 179, 220, 0.30) 0%, transparent 60%), radial-gradient(ellipse at 85% 20%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.30) 0%, transparent 50%), radial-gradient(ellipse at 60% 100%, rgba(25, 25, 25, 0.08) 0%, transparent 55%);"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
    <p
      class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-base-ink/50 mb-6 animate-zoom-in timeline-view animate-range-[entry_0%_cover_35%]"
    >
      ¿Listo para crecer?
    </p>
    <h2
      class="font-display text-[clamp(2.4rem,5vw,4rem)] font-bold leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.03em] text-base-ink mb-10 animate-fade-in-up timeline-view animate-range-[entry_0%_cover_45%]"
    >
      Tu competencia ya está<br />invirtiendo en su marca.<br />
      <span class="opacity-45">¿Y tú?</span>
    </h2>
    <div
      class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 items-center justify-center animate-fade-in-up timeline-view animate-range-[entry_15%_cover_55%]"
    >
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="inline-block bg-base-ink text-base-bg font-semibold text-[0.95rem] px-8 py-4 rounded-full transition-opacity duration-200 hover:opacity-80"
      >
        Hablemos de tu proyecto
      </a>
      <a
        href="/servicios"
        class="inline-block border-[1.5px] border-base-ink text-base-ink font-semibold text-[0.95rem] px-8 py-4 rounded-full transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-base-ink/[0.07]"
      >
        Ver servicios →
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
